&lt;a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/26/01/28/apple-creator-studio-review-incredible-value-for-most-creative-pros"&gt;first introduced&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;p&gt;in late January. Impressively, nearly all of the apps included within the bundle have received some form of update.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;|&lt;/p&gt;

